OL,5,G1730 Week In Review
OL,6,     FWeek In Review looks back at the
OL,7,     Fmain local, national and
OL,8,     Finternational stories of the week.
OL,9,G1800 The Chase
OL,10,     FFour players answer trivia
OL,11,     Fquestions. Then as a team, face a
OL,12,     Fquiz champion (The Chaser) to win
OL,13,     Fthousands of pounds in a timed
OL,14,     Ffinal quiz. Bradley Walsh hosts.
OL,15,G1900 Help Me Buy A Home
OL,16,     FLiz faces a tough challenge in
OL,17,     FGalway for young newlyweds, while
OL,18,     Fa solo-buyer and nurse seeks a
OL,19,     Fplace for respite in Dublin. PJ
OL,20,     Fand Kevin head to Leitrim to
OL,21,     Fexplore a Tiny House.
